        "intro-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A Celebration of Local Flavors",
            "size": "4xl"
          }
        },
        "intro-text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>What started as a shared dream between two chefs has grown into one of the city's most beloved dining destinations. At Saffron, every dish tells a story — of the farmer who grew the heirloom tomatoes, the fisherman who caught the morning's halibut, and the hands that shaped the pasta by hand.</p><p>We believe great food is about more than what's on the plate. It's about the people around the table, the conversations that linger, and the moments that become memories.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false
          }
        },
        "intro-button": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "link": {
              "text": "About Us",
              "href": "about.html",
              "target": "_self"
            },
            "style": "secondary",
            "size": "medium"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["intro-eyebrow", "intro-heading", "intro-text", "intro-button"]
    },
    "featured_dishes": {
      "type": "priced-list",
      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "From the Kitchen",
        "title": "Seasonal Highlights",
        "description": "A taste of what's on our menu this season — crafted daily with the freshest local ingredients.",
        "heading_alignment": "center",
        "layout": "single-column",
        "color_scheme": "standard"
      },
      "blocks": {
        "dish-1": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "name": "Roasted Beet & Burrata",
            "description": "<p>Heirloom beets, creamy burrata, toasted hazelnuts, and a honey-thyme vinaigrette. A vibrant starter that sets the tone.</p>",
            "price": "$18"
          }
        },
        "dish-2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "name": "Pan-Seared Halibut",
            "description": "<p>Wild-caught halibut over a bed of saffron risotto, with roasted fennel and a lemon-caper beurre blanc.</p>",
            "price": "$38"
          }
        },
        "dish-3": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "name": "Braised Lamb Shank",
            "description": "<p>Slow-braised for eight hours with root vegetables, red wine, and fresh rosemary. Served with creamy polenta.</p>",
            "price": "$34"
          }
        },
        "dish-4": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "name": "Dark Chocolate Fondant",
            "description": "<p>Warm chocolate cake with a molten center, served with salted caramel gelato and candied orange peel.</p>",
            "price": "$14"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["dish-1", "dish-2", "dish-3", "dish-4"]
    },
